The though for this project is to have a robot have the ability to play catch with a baseball with an individual. 
Sports now a days are centered on self motivation. However, for an only child, this limits them significantly. 
With this robot, it will even the odds and give only child children the ability to practice on their own. 

BUILD:
1) Robotic Vision to detect ball movement and color. 
2) Ball receiver to store the ball thrown. 
3) Ball shooter to shoot ball back to user. 
4) A type of meassuring system that will enable the robot to calculate how far the user is from the contraption to throw ball back to user. 
5) Fast moving motors to perform calculations to catch ball. 
